With Tailwind 3 this works:

```css
.custom {
    @apply grid gap-6;
}
```

```html
<div class="custom md:gap-y-8">
```

With Tailwind 4.0.1 the `md:gap-y-8` doesn't work, but it works if I use `!`, why?

- app.css:

```css
@import 'tailwindcss';

