**Describe your issue**

The [example from the docs](https://tailwindcss.com/docs/hover-focus-and-other-states#registering-a-custom-variant):

```css
@custom-variant pointer-coarse {
  @media (pointer: coarse) {
    @slot;
  }
}
```

Generates this CSS:

```css
.pointer-coarse\:text-black {
  @media (pointer: coarse) {
    color: var(--color-black);
  }
}
```

But it should be the other way around:

```diff
-.pointer-coarse\:text-black {
-  @media (pointer: coarse) {
+@media (pointer: coarse) {
+  .pointer-coarse\:text-black {
    color: var(--color-black);
  }
}
```

